text: At Hillion KopiTiam, another halal Halim Fish soup stall. Great stopover makan to venture great soup taste. Due to eating 🍽️ inside conserving air condition good thing to have milky Fish soup noodle. Innovative way mixing condensed milk upon request. Best taste of its kind😋

Very bad. Usually ordered from this store but their soup gradually becomes very salty. Yesterday I ordered salmon fish soup, only 4 SMALL thine pieces or fish… I can’t even feel the fish taste from it. Very bad, won’t come anymore
